shared_text:
Cuddeback Parent Teacher Organization
May 7 at 7:43 AM ·

Dear Cuddeback Teachers,

We love you.
We miss you.
We appreciate you.

I think we speak for all of us when we say, THANK YOU! Thank you for all that you do. Being a Cuddeback kid is something to be proud of and it’s the teachers and the staff that help shape our kids into kind, loving, smart, brave and happy kids. Your kindness and love for each student doesn’t go unnoticed. Thank you for making a positive impact on our children.

We hope you enjoyed some extra love this week, you deserve it.

Happy Teacher Appreciation Week! 💚

- Cuddeback PTO & Cuddeback Families

#teacherappreciationweek
#cuddebackkids
#thankyou
#wemissyou
